  <h3>TL;DR, Keka for Indian companies</h3>
  <p>The most modern Indian-built HRMS in 2026. Hyderabad team, used by 8,500+ companies. AI chatbot handles routine HR queries, automated onboarding, OKRs, 360-degree feedback, and full Indian payroll compliance (PF, ESI, PT, TDS, gratuity). Pricier than greytHR for compliance-only needs; cheaper than global tools for full HR stack.</p>
